    <Folder>
      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The Department of War has seen a significant increase in AI usage, with the undersecretary for research and engineering reporting a 1,775% rise. This shift is likely to enhance operational efficiency and decision-making processes across various military branches. The annual publication &#39;INSIGHT&#39; continues its focus on drone support, while the transition of &#39;Strategic Insights&#39; from weekly to monthly releases suggests an increased need for strategic intelligence dissemination.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
    </Folder>
